          span.cws-text Covid with strangers is where five-ish strangers sit at home with a Host to have a two hour conversation. The host pics a theme but the conversation can go anywhere from there! 
          span.cws-text You're meant to know pretty much nothing about the people that come, aside from the fact that they all signed up for this â€” just like you. It's self-selecting in that sense. Have fun with and make some new friends!
